chardsaltoun.com',NULL),(319,'2016-07-01 15:44:48','2016-07-01 15:44:48','79 Beak Street W1F 9SU London','Riflemaker is a contemporary art space in London co-founded in 2004 by Virginia Damtsa and Tot Taylor. The gallery exhibits and represents emerging artists as well as the historical artists who may have inspired them. It has been widely praised for its innovative programme.\n\nHoused within an historic gunmaker\'s workshop off Regent Street, W1F 9SU (built 1712 - the oldest public building in the west end) the gallery has worked closely with English Heritage to preserve this unique architectural building. Music and film events, talks/discussions and performance are held on Monday evenings.',NULL,0,51.5129059,'79 Beak Street W1F 9SU London',-0.136477199999945,'Riflemaker','Monday - Friday : 11:00 - 19:00, Saturday : 12:00 - 18:00',NULL,2,'www.riflemaker.org',NULL),(320,'2016-07-01 15:44:48','2016-07-01 15:44:48','Unit 8, 80A Ashfield St E1 2BJ London','Contemporary Art Gallery ',NULL,0,51.5167618,'Unit 8, 80A Ashfield St E1 2BJ London',-0.0576524000000518,'Ritter/Zamet','Wednesday - Saturday : 12:00 - 18:00, or by appointment',NULL,2,'www.ritterzamet.com',NULL),(321,'2016-07-01 15:44:48','2016-07-01 15:44:48','83 Page Street SW1P 4HA London','Contemporary Art Gallery ',NULL,0,51.4937812,'83 Page Street SW1P 4HA London',-0.130976299999929,'Rob Tufnell','Thursday - Saturday : 12:00 - 18:00, or by appointment',NULL,2,'http://www.robtufnell.com/index.html',NULL),(322,'2016-07-01 15:44:48','2016-07-01 15:44:48','38 Dover Street W1S 4NL London','Contemporary Art Gallery ',NULL,0,51.5084152,'38 Dover Street W1S 4NL London',-0.142496700000038,'Robilant + Voena','Monday - Friday : 10:00 - 18:00',NULL,2,'www.robilantvoena.com',NULL),(323,'2016-07-01 15:44:48','2016-07-01 15:44:48','4-6 Sheep Lane E8 4QS London','Contemporary Art Gallery ',NULL,0,51.5350485,'4-6 Sheep Lane E8 4QS London',-0.0601182999999992,'Rocket','See the website for further details',NULL,2,'www.rocketga